---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="pt-8 md:p-8 text-center bg-gray-50 font-sans flex flex-col items-center min-h-screen">
        <a href="/" class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 hover:opacity-80 transition">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="Goaly Logo" class="h-20 w-auto" />
        </a>
		<div class="max-w-3xl w-full bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-12 rounded-none md:rounded-2xl shadow-none md:shadow-sm border-t md:border border-gray-100 text-left flex-grow md:flex-none">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800">Terms of Service for Goaly</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> March 21, 2026</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Welcome to Goaly. By accessing or using our application ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please do not use Goaly.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">1. Description of Service</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Goaly is a productivity tool designed to help you track your goals by scheduling them directly onto your Google Calendar. We have designed the Service to operate with a minimal digital footprint:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>No Data Storage:</strong> We do not store, keep, or harvest your personal data. We do not maintain a central database of your goals, events, or personal information.</li>
                <li><strong>No Tracking:</strong> There is no analytics, tracking, or profiling of any kind within the application.</li>
                <li><strong>Session Only:</strong> The application only saves your active session to authenticate you and sets events on your Google Calendar on your behalf.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">2. User Responsibilities</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>Google Calendar Account:</strong> To use Goaly, you must have an active and valid Google account with access to Google Calendar.</li>
                <li><strong>Account Security:</strong> You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your Google account credentials and for all activities that occur under your account while using Goaly.</li>
                <li><strong>Acceptable Use:</strong> You agree to use Goaly solely for its intended purpose. You must not use the Service for any unlawful purpose or in any way that violates Google's own Terms of Service.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">3. Privacy and Data Handling</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Our commitment to your privacy is absolute. Because we do not store your data, your goals and calendar events remain entirely within your Google account infrastructure. Goaly's access is strictly limited to creating, modifying, and tracking the specific goal-related events you authorize.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Because Goaly functions as an intermediary tool that operates directly on your Google Calendar without storing your data on our servers, our liability is strictly limited:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 text-gray-700 space-y-2">
                <li><strong>"As Is" Service:</strong> Goaly is provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without any warranties of any kind, either express or implied.</li>
                <li><strong>No Liability for Data Loss:</strong> We are not responsible or liable for any loss, corruption, or accidental deletion of calendar events, goals, or associated data on your Google account.</li>
                <li><strong>Third-Party Dependencies:</strong> We are not liable for any service interruptions, data inaccuracies, or failures caused by the Google Calendar API or changes to Google's services.</li>
                <li><strong>General Limitation:</strong> In no event shall Goaly or its creators be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising out of or in connection with your use of the Service.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">5. Changes to the Terms</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms of Service at any time. Any changes will be reflected by an updated "Effective Date" at the top of this document. Your continued use of Goaly after any such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms of Service.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-gray-800">6. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">If you have any questions or concerns regarding these Terms of Service, please reach out to the project maintainers through <a href="https://github.com/gandazgul/goaly/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Github</a>.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
